hadowknight.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=281.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Soul Abrasion/Spell Casting Fury</span><hr size=1> Well when you have spell casting fury and you proc with shroud of death (and have no soul abrasion points) you crit and proc for 66 dmg rather than 50 damage.  I am pretty sure they are intended to work together, but  you never know heh. <p> ----------- <br>Ralanan Blackened<br>Human Grave Lord</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#E5E5E6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/uburtha.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Burtha</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>w4nn4b3!</span><br> <font color=#000033>(2/16/02 9:44:26 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylumshadowknight.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=281.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Soul Abrasion/Spell Casting Fury</span><hr size=1> I read at the sk website that soul abrasion gives you an extra 25, 50, and 100 at levels 1,2 and 3 for shroud of death.  So thats 150 at level 3.  With the spell casting fury that would give you a nice round 200 assuming a 33 percent increase. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br>Only cost you 18 points for level 3.<br><br>Burtha<br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#D5D4D5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/ukaedian.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kaedian</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.silentavengers.net/pictures/kaedian/smallskull.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Cyber Pimp</span><br> <font color=#000033>(2/16/02 11:53:37 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylumshadowknight.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=281.topic&in